-- Blackstone, Bain Capital May Bid for RBS Unit, Sunday Times Says
-- B y   E m m a   C h a r l t o n
-- 2012-07-15T08:51:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-15/blackstone-bain-capital-may-bid-for-rbs-unit-sunday-times-says.html
Blackstone Group LP (BX)  and Bain Capital
Partners LLC are preparing to bid for  Royal Bank of Scotland
Group Plc (RBS) ’s Direct Line Insurance Plc unit at the end of July,
the  Sunday Times  reported, citing people it didn’t identify.  KKR & Co., Apax Partners LLP and BC Partners Ltd. are also
considering a bid, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
